    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation with plenty of potential for someone who appreciates a practical buy. It shows its age and is best suited for a budget-minded driver, first-time buyer, or weekend project shopper looking for straightforward value. Priced to sell and presented with honest appeal, this is a great opportunity to secure inexpensive mobility without overpaying.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and honest little runner that could be a great fit for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra car. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it has character and offers solid value for the money. If you\u2019re looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a proven powertrain layout and plenty of life for the next owner who appreciates mechanical simplicity. It shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers dependable point-A-to-B duty, a comfortable cabin, and the kind of straightforward serviceability enthusiasts look for. Good candidate for a daily beater, starter car, or weekend clean-up project. Priced to reflect condition while still offering strong value for an affordable, usable car.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Cosmetic wear, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Not every car is about perfection\u2014some are about possibility. This one has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons: a machine with stories in its bones and plenty of life left for the right buyer. Whether you\u2019re hunting for a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or a dependable set of wheels with grit and soul, this car offers a chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank. If you appreciate charm, potential, and value, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
