      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. An ideal option for someone seeking an affordable daily driver, backup vehicle, or practical project, it presents a straightforward opportunity at an accessible price point. If you want inexpensive wheels without the premium cost, this one is worth a look.",
